{"tid":430205,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"記住 真的不要為了自己的伴侶 去刻意改變自己","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T02:22:10.000Z","uid":87396,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"23364ef7e0a7829b935a8b2696e5e14e561afaea","tid":430205,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"人往往拍咗拖後 會迷失左自己 為左佢 改變自己一切<br />\n其實咁樣真係唔岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做回自己 <br />\n我相信如果佢真係愛你嘅<br />\n你做返你自己 佢亦都會咁愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢愛嘅 係做回自己嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係謝檸檬教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不要刻意改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打 絲打們 <br />\n希望你地記住往後每次拍拖<br />\n做返自己就足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好麻目去改變"},{"pid":"5d8bafe15f36754ed6a93c6ddc4727528eba0f4f","tid":430205,"uid":87396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"雖然我知道連登仔好憎mk鋒 但係佢嚟首歌真係有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你地唔好盲反<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而愛得真心　叫世界目光也豔羨<br />\n並請不要去為誰擅作改變<br />\n好亦有缺點 不需特意改善<br />\n誰個也別要刻意改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4b836bd5669ad417e8c6081e6ba47727609a10","tid":430205,"uid":38545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"我真係完全迷失晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男友好喜歡大奶<br />\n自己身材又唔爭氣<br />\n又覺得我唔係佢心目中最靚<br />\n成日都覺得男友講某啲說話係嫌棄緊自己<br />\n為咗滿足佢食好多唔同藥<br />\n搞到自己好大壓力又好自卑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵個識得欣賞我成個人既人算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b036dddc64b3c2b78d8b02c5a3653a98ec329a3","tid":430205,"uid":